reviewText: I was very happy when it came in the mail when I popped the tape in at first it started acting weird I couldn't view the tape properly and I attempted to locate the distributor so I contacted them and told them the problems after I contacted them I attempted to view the tape again and the tape still proceeded to give me problems so then I changed tvs and the tape began to function properly I was so happy I emailed back to the distributor and gave them heads up on my tape working properly they ended up crediting my account and I was so happy my tape now works properly and I'm satisfied.
